11/09/2007
ANKARA, Turkey -- Parliament Speaker Koksal Toptan suggested on Monday (September 10th) that Turkey's support for the breakaway Turkish Republic of Northern Cyprus should be reduced, but he did not elaborate. 
He is making an official visit to northern Cyprus Tuesday to meet with Turkish Cypriot community leader Mehmet Ali Talat and Prime Minister Ferdi Sabit Soyer. 
(Milliyet - 11/09/07; Focus - 10/09/07)
